For the build you decided on React + Vite frontend, Supabase for database and auth, and Vercel for hosting. You're starting with a web app MVP before any native mobile app.

STEP 1:

Set up React Router with 4 pages: Dashboard, People, Gifts, and Ideas. 
Add a bottom nav bar that links between them. Use a warm coral accent 
colour (#D85A30). Mobile-first layout, max-width 420px centered. 
Clean, friendly aesthetic with rounded cards and warm white backgrounds.


